  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients at least 18 years old with a clinical diagnosis of Open-Angle Glaucoma for at
             least 6 months and currently treated with a monotherapy hypotensive medication

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Prior angle surgery in the study eye, severe visual field loss in either eye, and any
             other form of glaucoma besides open-angle glaucoma
      </textblock>
